red at that time.  This renewal authorized the repurchase of up to", "bbox": [93.8, 475.5, 1149.7, 498.6]}, {"text": "10,000,000 shares of the Company's common stock during the five-year period ending May 2017.  The Company repurchased", "bbox": [93.8, 500.5, 1154.7, 523.6]}, {"text": "3,870,248 shares under this authorization during 2014 for an average share price of $79.71. As of December 31, 2014, the", "bbox": [93.8, 525.5, 1149.5, 548.6]}, {"text": "approximate number of shares still available for repurchase under the May 2012 share repurchase authorization was 38,041.", "bbox": [93.8, 550.5, 1149.7, 573.6]}, {"text": "This authorization was canceled and replaced in January 2015 with a new standing share repurchase authorization approved by", "bbox": [93.8, 575.5, 1149.7, 598.6]}, {"text": "the Board of Directors, whereby the Company may repurchase up to 15,000,000 shares of its common stock over the following", "bbox": [93.8, 600.5, 1149.5, 623.6]}, {"text": "three years.", "bbox": [93.8, 625.5, 189.9, 648.6]}, {"text": "In November 2012, the Board of Directors approved a $1.0 billion share repurchase program authorizing repurchases of the", "bbox": [93.8, 675.5, 1149.5, 698.6]}, {"text": "Company's common shares over the following 12 to 18 months. In 2014, the Company completed this share repurchase program", "bbox": [93.8, 700.6, 1149.7, 723.6]}, {"text": "through an accelerated share repurchase transaction, whereby Dover paid $292,565 on March 10, 2014 to receive a variable", "bbox": [93.8, 725.6, 1149.7, 748.6]}, {"text": "number of shares on incremental dates through March 31, 2014. The Company repurchased 3,596,980 shares under this transaction", "bbox": [93.8, 750.6, 1149.7, 773.6]}, {"text": "for an average share price of $81.06.", "bbox": [93.8, 775.6, 409.8, 798.6]}, {"text": "20. Quarterly Data (Unaudited)", "bbox": [93.8, 825.6, 375.1, 848.7]}, {"text": "Continuing Operations", "bbox": [546.4, 894.0, 751.9, 917.1]}, {"text": "Net Earnings", "bbox":